<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Deal Posting Status Update</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #f5f7fa; 
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 20px auto; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #ffffff; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); 
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 30px; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .header h1 { 
            margin: 0; 
            font-size: 28px; 
            font-weight: 300; 
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .status-approved {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
        }
        .status-rejected {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
        }
        .status-pending {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #212529;
        }
        .content { 
            padding: 40px 30px; 
        }
        .greeting { 
            font-size: 18px; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            color: #2c3e50; 
        }
        .deal-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .deal-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
            gap: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #495057;
        }
        .message-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .message-box.success {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border-color: #c3e6cb;
        }
        .message-box.error {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border-color: #f5c6cb;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .footer { 
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
            padding: 30px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef; 
            color: #6c757d; 
        }
        .footer a { 
            color: #667eea; 
            text-decoration: none; 
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .next-steps h4 {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        }
        .next-steps ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .next-steps li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #424242;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { margin: 10px; }
            .header, .content, .footer { padding: 20px; }
            .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5px; }
            .btn { display: block; margin: 10px 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Deal Posting Status Update</h1>
            <div class="status-badge status-{{status}}">{{status}}</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{merchantName}},
            </div>

            <p>We have an update regarding your deal posting request.</p>

            <div class="deal-info">
                <h3>{{dealTitle}}</h3>
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <span class="info-label">Category:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{dealCategory}}</span>
                    <span class="info-label">Original Price:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">${{originalPrice}}</span>
                    <span class="info-label">Discounted Price:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">${{discountedPrice}}</span>
                    <span class="info-label">Submitted Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{submittedDate}}</span>
                    <span class="info-label">Status Updated:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{statusUpdateDate}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if approved}}
            <div class="message-box success">
                <h4>üéâ Congratulations! Your deal has been approved!</h4>
                <p>Your deal is now live and visible to all members. Customers can start redeeming this deal immediately.</p>
                {{#if adminMessage}}
                <p><strong>Admin Message:</strong> {{adminMessage}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>What happens next?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your deal is now active and available to customers</li>
                    <li>You'll receive notifications when customers request redemptions</li>
                    <li>Track your deal performance in the merchant dashboard</li>
                    <li>You can edit or update your deal anytime</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="{{dealUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">View Live Deal</a>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">Merchant Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if rejected}}
            <div class="message-box error">
                <h4>‚ùå Your deal posting request has been rejected</h4>
                <p>Unfortunately, your deal did not meet our current posting requirements.</p>
                {{#if rejectionReason}}
                <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{rejectionReason}}</p>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if adminMessage}}
                <p><strong>Admin Message:</strong> {{adminMessage}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>What can you do?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Review the feedback provided above</li>
                    <li>Modify your deal to address the concerns</li>
                    <li>Submit a new deal posting request</li>
                    <li>Contact support if you need clarification</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="{{createDealUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">Create New Deal</a>
                <a href="{{supportUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if pending}}
            <div class="message-box">
                <h4>‚è≥ Your deal is still under review</h4>
                <p>Our team is currently reviewing your deal posting request. This process typically takes 1-2 business days.</p>
                {{#if adminMessage}}
                <p><strong>Admin Message:</strong> {{adminMessage}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>While you wait:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Ensure your business profile is complete</li>
                    <li>Prepare additional deals for submission</li>
                    <li>Check out our deal posting best practices</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for being a valued merchant partner!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The Platform Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:cards@indiansinghana.com">cards@indiansinghana.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>Email: cards@indiansinghana.com | Website: www.indiansinghana.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
